<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Supports for visualizing KPI information from OLAP data through OlapGauge</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Supports for viewing Value ToolTip, also called as "Pointer ToolTip".</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Supports for viewing Goal ToolTip, also called as "Marker ToolTip".</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Supports for choosing scenario to display reports through OlapGauge.</Paragraph></ListItem>
